casebody.data:
No. 234,

Misc.

Jackson v. Taylor, Acting Warden. Albert A. Carretta for petitioner. Solicitor General Rankin, Assistant Attorney General Olney, Beatrice Rosenberg and Carl H. Imlay for respondent.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit granted limited to the gross sentence question.
